               <sense xml:id="Dmain" xml:lang="la" source="#dillmann"> <gramGrp> <pos expand="not found">n. peregr.</pos> </gramGrp>, <lbl expand="scilicet">sc.</lbl> <foreign xml:lang="grc">φιάλη</foreign>, <lbl expand="pluralis">Pl.</lbl> <foreign xml:lang="gez">ፍያላት፡</foreign> et <foreign xml:lang="gez">ፍየላት፡</foreign>, <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><quote> phiala </quote></cit>, <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><quote> crater </quote></cit>: <foreign xml:lang="gez">አሐዱ፡ ፍያል፡ ዘብሩር፡</foreign> <ref cRef="Num. " loc="7,13">Num.  7,13</ref> <lbl expand="sequens">seq.</lbl>; <foreign xml:lang="gez">ፍያላት፡</foreign> <ref cRef="Ex." loc="27,3">Ex. 27,3</ref>; <ref cRef="Ex." loc="28,23">Ex. 28,23</ref>; <ref cRef="Num." loc="4,14">Num. 4,14</ref>; <ref cRef="1 Esr." loc="2,12">1 Esr. 2,12</ref>; <ref cRef="2 Esr." loc="17,70">2 Esr. 17,70</ref>; <ref cRef="Prov." loc="23,31">Prov. 23,31</ref>; <foreign xml:lang="gez">ፍየላት፡</foreign> et <foreign xml:lang="gez">ፍያላት፡</foreign> <ref cRef="Jer." loc="52,18">Jer. 52,18</ref>; <ref cRef="3 Reg." loc="7,26">3 Reg. 7,26</ref>; <ref cRef="3 Reg." loc="7,31">3 Reg. 7,31</ref>; <ref cRef="4 Reg. " loc="12,13">4 Reg.  12,13</ref>. „Aethiopes vero <foreign xml:lang="gez">ፍያል፡</foreign> de porcellaneis seu Chinensibus poculis tantum interpretantur, quae nos Latine murrhina vascula dici posse putamus“ Lud. <cb n="1378" xml:id="c1378"/> </sense>
               
